 supplementary videos, see:\nhttps://fsadeghi.github.io/Sim2RealViewInvariantServo\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Dec 2017 18:54:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-21"}
